{"tid":1319877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"畫家再申保釋被拒　辯方：土生土長 朋友是最大財產不會潛逃","createTime":"2019-07-15T09:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:04:06.000Z","uid":242903,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cdcf01a64a3931f2c86468c96dd0da036c80ca5d","tid":1319877,"uid":242903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"畫家再申保釋被拒　辯方：土生土長　<span style=\"font-size: large;\">朋友是最大財產不會潛逃</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人稱「畫家」的潘浩超（前名為潘運瑭），因參與包圍警察總部等反送中示威活動，被控襲警、刑事毀壞和在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序，7 月 2 日被捕後不准保釋一直還押，他今日作保釋覆核，辯方指他在土生土長，最大的財產就是在香港認識的朋友，不會潛逃，但裁判官認為他有機會棄保潛逃，拒絕他保釋。<br />\n<br />\n31 歲的潘浩超 6.21 包圍警總期間，涉嫌襲擊警員、損毀警總的外牆和扶手電梯、用粗口罵警員，呼籲其他示威者提供雞蛋給他掟警員等，被控三項控罪，他的保釋覆核被拒後，要繼續還押，下月 2 日上庭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%86%8D%E7%94%B3%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9-%E5%9C%9F%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%9F%E9%95%B7-%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B2%A1%E7%94%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%BD%9B%E9%80%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%259C%259F%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%259F%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%2594%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25BD%259B%25E9%2580%2583%2F&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdt%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=76c6d6d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%259C%259F%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%259F%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B2%25